snippet.title: UFL™ Developer Diary Series #3 | Equipment
snippet.description:
The long-awaited return of #UFLDevDiary is here! In this episode we'll talk about an important stuff that makes every football game more enjoyable and bright ⚽ 
Be ready for a big amount of beauty 😍

We are now changing the format of our #UFLDevDiary to allow our community get a closer look at the development process. The new format is already in production. Stay tuned!

UFL™ is a global online football league where only your skills matter. Join the revolution changing the world of football simulation forever today! ⬇️
https://joinufl.com
